%% Diagram: Layout thrashing - interleaved reads vs batched
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant JS as JavaScript
    participant Pending as Pending mutations
    participant Engine as Style + Layout

    Note over JS,Engine: BAD — interleaved read after write
    loop For each item N
        JS->>Engine: read offsetWidth
        Engine-->>JS: flushes pending styles + layout
        JS->>Pending: write item.style.width
    end

    Note over JS,Engine: GOOD — batch reads, then writes
    JS->>Engine: read offsetWidth once
    Engine-->>JS: single flush
    loop For each item N
        JS->>Pending: write item.style.width
    end
    Pending-->>Engine: flush at next frame boundary
